Published in 1919, it marked the first individual cartoon collection in China. The works therein expressed the author's political attitude and patriotism towards the crisis of the nation, survival of the homeland and various social phenomena at that time and reflected his determination to fight with cartoon as the weapon. The entire book was embraced and loved by people with its easy-to-understand representation and vivid and true-to-life portrayal. It stirred up people's love for the country, which was exactly what this cartoon book was valuable for.

[[zh:國恥畫譜]]

